    <Fragment slot="content">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-3xl mb-2">About me</h2>
      <p>
        I am a technology enthusiast with immense intellectual curiosity. I have experience working in teams and I focus on backend development technologies. However, I am always willing to expand to other IT areas.
        <br />
        <br />
